label: A3B2_oP20_62_3c_2c-001
title: Stibnite (Sb$_{2}$S$_{3}$, $D5_{8}$) Structure
comments:
Some authorities list Th$_{2}$S$_{3}$ or P$_{2}$Hf$_{3}$ as the prototype, but we will use the mineral with the {\em Strukturbericht} designation. 
 This structure has the same AFLOW label, A3B2\_oP20\_62\_3c\_2c, as \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B2_oP20_62_3c_2c-002}{Pt$_{2}$Ge$_{3}$} and \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B2_oP20_62_3c_2c-003}{ottemannite (Sn$_{2}$S$_{3}$)}. The structures are generated by the same symmetry operations with different sets of parameters ({\tt --params}) specified in their corresponding CIF files.
